PN,38501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FA Guernsey landlord says she has spent
OL,7,Fnearly #20,000 trying to get her
OL,8,Ftenant evicted.
OL,10,FFallon Bewey says the renter refused
OL,11,Fto leave her property in November last
OL,12,Fyear at the end of a one-year
OL,13,Fagreement, which she decided not to
OL,14,Frenew.
OL,16,FMs Bewey had to turn to the courts,
OL,17,Fwhich have given the tenant a stay of
OL,18,Feviction until June.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FThis means that, by the time the
OL,7,Frenter is forced to leave, she will
OL,8,Fnot have had access to her property
OL,9,Ffor nearly eight months past the end
OL,10,Fof the original agreement.
OL,12,FMs Bewey, a working mother of two,
OL,13,Fbelieves the courts prioritise tenants
OL,14,Fover landlords.
OL,16,FShe explains: "Not every landlord on
OL,17,Fthe island is a career landlord.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,F"There are many situations where
OL,7,Fpeople have rental properties due to
OL,8,Fpersonal circumstances, such as the
OL,9,Fbreakdown of marriages, and there are
OL,10,Fmany pensioners who have it as their
OL,11,Fmain source of income.
OL,13,F"Going through the courts is costly
OL,14,Fand time-consuming, and it's really
OL,15,Fconcerning that it can cost a landlord
OL,16,Fwho hasn't broken the agreement tens
OL,17,Fof thousands of pounds."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FIn Guernsey, if a tenant decides not
OL,7,Fto leave a property they have been
OL,8,Ftold to vacate, their landlord has to
OL,9,Fapply to the Royal Court for a
OL,10,Fsummons, where a judge then reviews an
OL,11,Fapplication for eviction.
OL,13,FIf this is opposed, a hearing can be
OL,14,Fcalled before Jurats, which, even if
OL,15,Fsuccessful, can lead to a tenant being
OL,16,Fgiven up to six months to find
OL,17,Fsomewhere else to go.
OL,19,FThe legal fees can escalate quickly
OL,20,Fand Ms Bewey says it is not a level
OL,21,Fplaying field.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FShe explains she has encountered
OL,7,Ffurther problems with Guernsey's
OL,8,Frental system, such as tenants not
OL,9,Fhaving to tell their landlord they
OL,10,Fwill be staying in a property, which
OL,11,Fcan leave future renters who are
OL,12,Fexpecting to move in stranded.
OL,14,FStays of eviction also come with
OL,15,Fconditions, which Ms Bewey believes
OL,16,Fher tenant has broken.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FHowever, her only means of recourse is
OL,7,Fto turn once again to the courts and
OL,8,Fpay more fees, despite maintaining
OL,9,Fthat she has not breached the
OL,10,Fagreement.
OL,12,FMs Bewey adds: "I don't feel supported
OL,13,Fby the courts or police whatsoever.
OL,15,F"The tenancy agreement, which I
OL,16,Fbelieve to be legally binding, was not
OL,17,Fenforced at all by the courts, and
OL,18,Fthey were not interested that the
OL,19,Ftenancy had been breached.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,F"The housing crisis in Guernsey means
OL,7,Fthat stays of eviction are issued
OL,8,Fbased on the ability for a tenant to
OL,9,Ffind alternative accommodation,
OL,10,Fmeaning the responsibility for this
OL,11,Fproblem falls on the landlord."
OL,13,FThe States are looking at changing the
OL,14,Fcurrent legislation to provide more
OL,15,Fstringent checks on tenants'
OL,16,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FDeputy David Dorrity, from Guernsey's
OL,7,FHousing Committee, says: "Anybody who
OL,8,Fgets a stay of eviction will have to
OL,9,Fshow that towards the end of their
OL,10,Fnotice period, they were actively
OL,11,Flooking for alternative accommodation.
OL,13,F"There may also be the creation of a
OL,14,Ftribunal to decide on matters where
OL,15,Fthere's a tenancy dispute."
OL,17,FJersey is also set to see changes to
OL,18,Fits rental rules, with the Residential
OL,19,FTenancy Amendment Law set to come into
OL,20,Feffect later this year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FThe new legislation will strengthen
OL,7,Frenters' rights on the island, but
OL,8,Fwill also include protections for
OL,9,Flandlords, such as the ability to give
OL,10,Fshorter notice periods to tenants who
OL,11,Fhave caused damage to a property.
OL,13,FHowever, the fundamental process of
OL,14,Fevicting a tenant is currently, and
OL,15,Fwill remain, similar to the process in
OL,16,FGuernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FJersey's Housing Minister, Sam Mezec,
OL,7,Fexplains: "Hopefully, tenants respect
OL,8,Fthe notice periods their landlord
OL,9,Fgives them, but if they don't,
OL,10,Flandlords can go to the Petty Debts
OL,11,FCourt to seek an eviction order
OL,12,Fenacted by the Viscount's office.
OL,14,F"Thankfully, cases getting to the
OL,15,Fcourt are rare, but they can be very
OL,16,Fdifficult.
OL,26,@nD@arr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,F"A tenant may be desperately trying to
OL,7,Ffind other housing and haven't been
OL,8,Fable to, in which case the Petty Debts
OL,9,FCourt can give them a stay of eviction
OL,10,Fand grant them some extra time to do
OL,11,Fso."
OL,13,FLaws in the Channel Islands are
OL,14,Flargely in line with those in the UK
OL,15,Fat present, as landlords there must
OL,16,Falso apply to the courts for
OL,17,Fpossession orders to evict tenants.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773173476
OL,3,CLandlord spends nearly #20,000 trying
OL,4,Cto evict tenant at end of lease
OL,6,FIf this is obtained and a tenant still
OL,7,Frefuses to leave, a landlord can apply
OL,8,Ffor a warrant, enabling bailiffs to
OL,9,Fphysically enforce evictions.
OL,11,FUK rules are also about to get notably
OL,12,Fstricter compared to those in the
OL,13,FChannel Islands, as the Renters'
OL,14,FRights Act will ban no-fault evictions
OL,15,Ffrom 1 May.
OL,17,FThe Act will require landlords to
OL,18,Fprovide "reasonable grounds" for
OL,19,Fsomeone to leave, and at least four
OL,20,Fmonths' notice, after a minimum rental
OL,21,Fperiod of 12 months.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
